					<description><!--[CDATA[<p-->Regenerative Medicine Minnesota (RMM) has awarded funding to 10 high-impact projects aimed at accelerating the development of breakthrough therapies that restore, replace or regenerate damaged cells, tissues and organs. Co-led by the University of Minnesota and Mayo Clinic, Regenerative Medicine Minnesota brings together the state's leading research institutions to advance regenerative medicine and improve patient […]<p></p>
