		<title>Mayo Clinic study finds wearable data may help predict patient engagement in remote COPD rehabilitation</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-study-finds-wearable-data-may-help-predict-patient-engagement-in-remote-copd-rehabilitation/
		
